div.p: This Observation contains all references to all the observations and exam information related to an exam that is not one of the predefined types (i.e. not an US, MG, NM, etc).
As of this ballot, the child observations of a US Exam have not been defined. They will be defined in a later ballot.
This graph provides an overview of this profile, and its dependencies.
Click on any of the elements of the graph to go to a section describing that element.
